title: Israel Launches Operation to Destroy Hezbollah Tunnels on Lebanese Border
originSummary: Israel has initiated an operation to demolish tunnels constructed by Hezbollah along the Lebanese border.
The operation aims to neutralize the threat posed by these tunnels and enhance security in the region.
The operation highlights the ongoing tensions between Israel and Hezbollah, a militant group based in Lebanon.
